Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:17.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For one to fully comprehend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This Pony fascination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:19.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let me first sum up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The previous of Pony generations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Generation One appeared on TV in the 80s
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It was made to sell toys
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Plots were hardly very weighty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:28.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And Generation Two
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I do not mean to grouse and gripe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But these characters fall right into the "girly" stereotypes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:35.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And Generation Three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is just too awful and too tragic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So let's jump to number Four
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where Friendship Is Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All the characters compelling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the stellar storytelling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:49.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the lovely animation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:51.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brought about great dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This is where we meet the Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For they like My Little Pony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:56.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes, the bros enjoy the ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So let's go and meet the Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well the growth in Pony fandom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:11.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Might simply seem absurd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:13.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,True fans adore the show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,While others gallop to the Herd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:15.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For hipster Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:17.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Watching pastel ponies has appeal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Though first it seems ironic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Soon enough it's very real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:22.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For Moderates they start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With how they're finding it through hype
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When the Bronies they'd invade
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Their favorite forums and websites
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:28.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And though first a little skeptical
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:29.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These Moderates inquired
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And once they finally saw the show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Their love for it caught fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The core of the meetups
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:35.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And conventions that you see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:36.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are the social groups that come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To BronyCon and Everfree
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:40.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Moderates and Hipsters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:41.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are the big groups of the Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:42.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They're the dudes that are the bulk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of all the men who like the ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Creative Bronies are the final bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:01:59.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Making music, art and stories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All inspired by the show
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:04.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,While counting down the days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From Season One to Season Two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The musicians wrote funky little songs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like Pinkie's Brew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:12.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Pony Generators churn out many new OCs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the artists put their art
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,On TUMBLR blogs for all to see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:16.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The writers pair their favorites
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:17.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Voicing charming little quips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And although they face some critics
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The will go down with their ships
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Their talent is their glory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ever growing, never stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From the music to the stories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the artwork and the clopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:29.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But let's steer away from that one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And get right back to the ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For Creatives are the final bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In the wacky world of Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Creatives, and Moderates
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And lastly Hipster Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are the groups that are quite proud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:46.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To watch the show
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My Little Pony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hey! Forgetting somepony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It seems your little lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Left the fairer sex neglected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well, when girls like little ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That's very much expected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even so, you can't ignore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These fillies' contributions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We're involved in Brony culture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And we demand our inclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We attend all the conventions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Create art and music too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We discuss the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Talk on forums
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Everything that these dudes do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, we're not bros,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But we're Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Though some prefer Pegasisters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And we also are Creatives
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Moderates, and even Hipsters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well, there you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All the Bronies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:47.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Anypony else I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now, if it's all the same to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Class dismissed!